reviewText: It's ok. Was more about sunken ships than anything else.
Love it wish it as more.

This particular 2 DVD set arrived quickly as promised and was very well done. I showed it to my 6th grade science class but unfortunately did not preview it in order to prepare my kids that there were some mating scenes. Otherwise, Bravo on a job well done!
My students enjoyed this.  It was very informative.

I bought this DVD for my austist grandson who loves fish and sharks and any kind of underwater  sea animals.when he gets fussy and a little tired I can put this on and he will watch it and it calms him down,sometime he will even fall asleep while watching it.he is five years old. I plan on ordering some more like it
